        {
            "title": "港股開跌181點  ASMPT逆升2.9%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股恒生指數開跌181點或0.7%，報25733，恒生科技指數跌38點或0.8%，報4826點 ; 恒生國企指數跌52點或0.6%，報8680點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">大市成交29.26億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：ASMPT官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230726_FI_-source_web_ASMPT.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：ASMPT官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230726_FI_-source_web_ASMPT.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：ASMPT官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ASMPT(00522)升2.91%，報159元，首季業績及次季指引超預期，投行唱好。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">瀾起科技(06809)升4.97%，報241元，成交入20大。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">寧德(03750)升1.85%，報715.5元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">萬洲(00288)跌2.54%，報10.34元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">騰訊(00700)跌1.66%，報487元; 阿里巴巴(09988)跌1.76%，報128.1元。</p>\n</div>",
